<ElliciumText TextStyle="TextStyle.H2" TagName="TagName.H1" class="rz-pt-8">
    DataGrid <strong>Virtualization</strong>
</ElliciumText>
<ElliciumText TextStyle="TextStyle.Subtitle1" TagName="TagName.P" class="rz-pb-4">
    Virtualization allows you to render large amounts of data on demand. The ElliciumDataGrid component uses Entity Framework to query the visible data.
</ElliciumText>
<ElliciumText TextStyle="TextStyle.Subtitle1" TagName="TagName.P" class="rz-pb-4">
    Just set the <code>AllowVirtualization</code> property to <code>true</code>. Requires .NET Core 5.0+.
</ElliciumText>

